node.text: Praying over you and all that concerns you. God’s got you!

node.text: Hell Shakers hang together. 💃 whose your friends? They say if you look at the five closest friends they are a prophecy into your future. I’m blessed with wonderful friends far and wide! Tag a friend to let them know you love and appreciate them. Show them love. The second picture I’m trying to talk them into doing a praise break with me 😂 we are in Columbus Georgia ready to see y’all tomorrow night at 7PM at Bridge Church! Hell shaker tank in my store www.RealTalkKim.com
